metadata.name: Liquid Chloride
metadata.description:
Just off Route 66, the canals that line Amboy Road south of Amboy Crater are filled with food grade liquid Calcium Chloride and water. This creates the most incredible hue of crystalline turquoise and toxic beauty.

Location  
National Chloride Company of America, Amboy, CA

Date of Capture: July 03, 2013  
NFT Edition of 12
